<!-- banner -->
<div class="banner">
  <h1>Hire Share</h1>
  <!-- buttons -->
  <div class="col-md-12">
    <div class="btn-group btn-custom">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-default"><%= link_to "Hire Equipment", items_path %></button>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-default dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
        <span class="caret"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Toggle Dropdown</span>
      </button>
      <ul class="dropdown-menu">
        <% Category.all.each do |c| %>
          <li><%= link_to c.name, items_path(category: c.name) %></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="btn-group" role="group">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-default"><%= link_to "List Equipment", new_item_path %></button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- service item -->
<div class="service-desc col-md-4">
	<h3>Make money.</h3>
	<p>
		What's the most expensive piece of equipment you own, which you haven't used
		in more than a month? You wouldn't let an employee or contractor sit around
		doing nothing for a month, so why let your equipment do it?
	</p>
</div>
<!-- end service item -->

<!-- service item -->
<div class="service-desc col-md-4">
	<h3>Pay less.</h3>
	<p>
		Equipment lease firms must charge high prices in order to justify their investment.
		By borrowing off those who own equipment for their own use, you can borrow at
		a lower cost, and both sides win.
	</p>
</div>
<!-- end service item -->

<!-- service item -->
<div class="service-desc col-md-4">
	<h3>Build sustainably.</h3>
	<p>
		Idle equipment is a waste of money and resources. By loaning and borrowing
		equipment, you can help save materials and energy. Save money, make money,
		 and reduce waste.
	</p>
</div>
<!-- end service item -->
<div class="home-footer">

</div>
